---
// Vision — Clean light theme
---

<section class="section" id="vision">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="vision-header">
      <div class="section-label animate-on-scroll">Our Vision</div>
      <h2 class="section-title animate-on-scroll">What is Embodied AI?</h2>
      <p class="vision-lead animate-on-scroll">
        Embodied AI represents the next frontier of artificial intelligence — agents that don't just process information, but perceive, reason, and act within the physical world. It bridges the gap between digital intelligence and real-world impact.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="pillars-grid">
      <div class="pillar glass-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="pillar-num">01</div>
        <h3>Perceive</h3>
        <p>Understanding the environment through vision, touch, spatial awareness, and multimodal sensing.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar glass-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="pillar-num">02</div>
        <h3>Reason</h3>
        <p>Building world models, planning actions, and making decisions based on goals and context.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar glass-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="pillar-num">03</div>
        <h3>Act</h3>
        <p>Executing physical actions through robots, virtual agents, or intelligent control systems.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar glass-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="pillar-num">04</div>
        <h3>Adapt</h3>
        <p>Learning continuously from feedback, transferring skills across tasks, scenes, and environments.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section quote-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="quote-content">
      <blockquote class="quote-block animate-on-scroll">
        <p>"We believe the next leap in AI will not come from bigger models alone, but from machines that learn through physical interaction — seeing, touching, and reasoning about the world as humans do."</p>
        <footer>
          <span class="quote-line"></span>
          <span>EAI LAB Alliance</span>
        </footer>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .vision-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 3.5rem;
  }

  .vision-header .section-label {
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .vision-header .section-label::before {
    display: none;
  }

  .vision-lead {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .pillars-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .pillar {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .pillar-num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .pillar h3 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .pillar p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Quote */
  .quote-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
  }

  .quote-content {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .quote-block {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .quote-block p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .quote-block footer {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .quote-line {
    width: 24px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 1px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .pillars-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .pillars-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .quote-block { padding: 2rem 1.25rem; }
    .quote-block p { font-size: 1rem; }
  }
</style>
